snippet: Two people suspected of being militants were killed when an improvised bomb that the police said was being prepared for a terrorist attack exploded in a mosque’s cemetery.
abstract: Two people suspected of being militants are killed when improvised bomb being prepared for terrorist attack explodes in village of Dugulubgey in Russia's North Caucasus region.
lead_paragraph: Two people suspected of being militants were killed when an improvised bomb that the police said was being prepared for a terrorist attack exploded in a mosque’s cemetery.

headline.main: Russia: 2 Bomb Makers Die, Police Say
